[{"id":"358eae26226753c1afad8e42e2351296","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: please fwd to Jeffrey","date":"2008-03-05T14:55:43.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 5, 2008","formatted_time":"2:55 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: bwjaeger310@aol.com [mailto:bwjaeger310@aol.com] \nSent: Wednesday, March 05, 2008 9:39 AM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: please fwd to Jeffrey\n\n \n\nJeffrey, \n\n \n\nIt was great seeing you a couple weeks ago at your office and Duncan and I appreciate your input and insight.  I hope that you are now comfortable with the initial capacity of $500mm for the strategy and we believe that as this arena grows, so to will the market.\n\n \n\nI understand that you are focused on more pressing matters at this time and when the dust settles, we can reconvene and move forward. In the meantime, I will keep you up any meaningful developments.  \n\n \n\nPlease let me know if I can be on any help over the coming weeks. I have known you for over 10 years and want everything to work out to your satisfaction.\n\n \n\nSincerely,\n\n________________________________\n\nSupercharge your AIM. Get the AIM toolbar <http://download.aim.com/client/aimtoolbar?NCID=aolcmp00300000002586>  for your browser. \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */